io.advantageous.qbit.service

Interface ServiceMethodHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Input, ReceiveQueueListener<MethodCall<java.lang.Object>>

    public interface ServiceMethodHandler
extends ReceiveQueueListener<MethodCall<java.lang.Object>>
    This is a plugin just for the piece that does the invocation. QBit has a boon implementation of this that uses reflection. One could, for example, plugin an implementation of this that used bytecode generation.

    Created by Richard on 9/8/14.
